            <h2>Biography</h2>
            <p>A R Rahman is an Indian composer, singer, and music producer who has garnered international acclaim for his work in film music. Born on January 6, 1967, in Chennai, India, he began his career in the early 1990s and quickly rose to prominence.</p>
