        <section>
            <h2>Awards and Recognition</h2>
            <p>Rahman has won numerous awards, including two Academy Awards, two Grammy Awards, a BAFTA Award, and a Golden Globe. His unique blend of Indian classical music with electronic music and world music has made him a pioneer in the industry.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Influence and Legacy</h2>
            <p>With a career spanning over three decades, A R Rahman has influenced a generation of musicians and composers. His contributions to music extend beyond films, as he has also worked on various humanitarian projects and has been an advocate for social causes.</p>
